the new lot is a 1943 british drama film directed by carol reed and starring eric ambler , robert donat , kathleen harrison , bernard lee , raymond huntley , john laurie , peter ustinov and austin trevor , with music by richard addinsell . the film follows five new recruits from different background and their experiences as they join the army . the film was later expanded and remade as the way ahead , co-written by ambler and ustinov , directed by carol reed , and starring david niven .